01:06:37.160 --> 01:06:38.640
I know Young's Red Book.

01:06:38.640 --> 01:06:41.080
I mean, I ran into it as you said.

01:06:41.080 --> 01:06:42.920
Because I have friends who are young and analysts.

01:06:42.920 --> 01:06:49.680
But I haven't run across any mention of Young in my reading about the surrealist painters.

01:06:49.680 --> 01:06:59.040
In his huge book, I don't know how many plates there are of his paintings of his dreams.

01:06:59.040 --> 01:07:01.240
