And from that it got, and the whole Picasso young thing that is talked about is very strong.

01:09:04.760 --> 01:09:07.800
But Bachelorette was a philosopher and he was a journalist.

01:09:07.800 --> 01:09:08.800
Yeah.

01:09:08.800 --> 01:09:09.800
But he was called the philosopher of surrealism.

01:09:09.800 --> 01:09:10.800
I love that.

01:09:10.800 --> 01:09:15.000
Also, the red book was only published in the last few years.

01:09:15.000 --> 01:09:16.000
That's true.

01:09:16.000 --> 01:09:17.000
But one of those.

01:09:17.000 --> 01:09:18.000
So nobody saw those.

