So I just want to ask a little bit about that.

01:17:15.240 --> 01:17:18.640
The relationship, if you know anything about the relationship with the painters and the

01:17:18.640 --> 01:17:24.200
word signs, does that come up in the language with the poets?

01:17:24.200 --> 01:17:30.640
Well, the Mihou and the Mihou and Waton, the constellatius and Mihou and the sign, very

01:17:30.640 --> 01:17:32.120
big there.

01:17:32.120 --> 01:17:34.440
But Mark probably can go on from.

