I mean, there was a lot of communication at a certain point, particularly in the late

01:19:32.920 --> 01:19:34.440
19th century.

01:19:34.440 --> 01:19:37.260
And so I think it's a continuum really.

01:19:37.260 --> 01:19:41.760
